ess and not through #Revolution. Details later: Vanguard The police have, Monday, arrested another SaharaReporters’ journalist, Victor Ogungbero. August 5, 2019 In "News" Publisher of SaharaReporters, an online news agency based in New York city, United States of America, Mr Omoyele Sowore, was yesterday arrested by the Police in Lagos ,over allegation of threat to life and blackmail on a London based journalist, Lekan Fatodu. January 12, 2017 In "News" SENATE President, Bukola Saraki, yesterday, said he lost the sum of N12 million from his administrative office in Kwara State to burglars two weeks ago. June 5, 2016 In "News"